<! [CDATA[
Agoda Logo
Agoda Company Pte. Ltd. and Agoda Travel Services Pte. Ltd., better known just as Agoda, is a Singaporean travel agency and online metasearch engine for hotels, vacation rentals, flights, and airport transfers. Headquartered at the Prudential Tower and Guoco Tower within the Downtown Core district of Singapore, it is currently a subsidiary of Booking Holdings. Agoda’s bookings are made via its website and mobile app which are available in 38 languages.
You can download theAgodalogo on full-version of the page.
